display="inline"><![CDATA[V\neq \{0\}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link
type="local"
href="vectsp-000O.xml"
addr="vectsp-000O"
title="Finite-Dimensional Vector Space">Finite-Dimensional Vector Space</fr:link> over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex>. Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[L\colon  V\to  V]]></fr:tex> be a linear operator. Then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[L]]></fr:tex> has at least one eigenvalue.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
